com.aionemu.gameserver.model.gameobjects
Class AionObject

java.lang.Object
  com.aionemu.gameserver.model.gameobjects.AionObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Item, Letter, PlayerAlliance, PlayerAllianceMember, PlayerGroup, VisibleObject
public abstract class AionObject
extends java.lang.Object

This is the base class for all "in-game" objects, that player can interact with, such as: npcs, monsters, players, items.

Each AionObject is uniquely identified by objectId.
